## Azure Infrastructure

The following Azure resources were deployed for the lab:

- Virtual Network
- Virtual Machine
- Network Security Group
- Public IP address
- Log Analytics Workspace
- Resource Group

![Azure Resources](screenshots/azure-resources.png)

---

## Security Log Investigation

Security logs were analyzed in Microsoft Sentinel using KQL queries.

The investigation focused on Windows security events such as failed login attempts.

![Sentinel Log Analysis](screenshots/sentinel-log-query.png)
